            <p class="text-small text-slate">State and Law (PiP) 9/2012, p. 18-30</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <p class="text-body text-navy font-medium">Constitutionalization of the Ne Bis In Idem Principle in Polish Legal Order</p>
