          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <p class="text-body text-navy font-medium">Hosting Operations on Data Covered by Exclusion of Liability</p>
            <p class="text-small text-slate">Legal Monitor 24/2009, p. 1333-1336</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-200">
            <p class="text-body text-navy font-medium">Protection of Acquired Rights and Economic Crisis</p>
